{"tid":2176944,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我地應該多搞幾次黑衫日，最好就一直維持","createTime":"2020-08-27T11:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T05:52:27.000Z","uid":211994,"like":144,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"91f592b0a30a0c3ef55a783334b095a28fa31344","tid":2176944,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:21:18.000Z","msg":"但比起喺重要日子著黑衫<br />\n我覺得定每個星期揀一日著黑衫會更好<br />\n例如逢星期日，因為以前好多大遊行都揀喺星期日<br />\n長久以來，我地嘅「<strong>黑色星期日</strong>」就會慢慢深深刻喺每個香港人腦中<br />\n雖然大家都話唔好習慣，但養成習慣去紀念呢啲事都唔係壞事<br />\n唔知大家點睇<br />\n<br />\n而特定日子就著黑衫+出嚟和你sing<br />\n我地亦都應該搞多啲靜默遊行，但記得要彩虹裝拉埋班藍絲落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40a92c7c479d72985c8f06520220f80d2d68b74","tid":2176944,"uid":44783,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:22:49.000Z","msg":"屋企九成都係黑衫<br />\n日日都著緊"},{"pid":"b8f569eedf9feb3a2419b7d98b8424bf81d005e3","tid":2176944,"uid":211994,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:22:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jtkf9ay.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtkf9ay.jpg&h=313dad73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee96b7ab859aa427400892b5afd7dbff1fdef87a","tid":2176944,"uid":82815,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:23:23.000Z","msg":"定逢星期幾都幾好"},{"pid":"b12b1e00bee1ecde46e836e8faa7b5312d726b47","tid":2176944,"uid":195350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:23:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"70b68288af09f6b4146d2cc4945d99364b4b141c","tid":2176944,"uid":68261,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:23:57.000Z","msg":"岩啦著黑衫完全冇成本"},{"pid":"5744731e47b11d744aad9036107956ea9bf5365d","tid":2176944,"uid":268547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:24:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0e436c7625e2fb022a63fb6dad4b5e7d6b5c97a3","tid":2176944,"uid":211994,"like":32,"dislike